Package: shinyStep
Type: Package
Title: Interactive Step Debugger for R Functions in Shiny Apps
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Han", "Zhang", email = "zhangh.ustc@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides Shiny modules that enable interactive, expression-by-expression
    debugging of registered R functions within a running Shiny application. Supports
    step-next, step-into (for/while/repeat/if/else blocks at any nesting depth),
    continue-to-next-pause, and in-frame console evaluation.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: false
Imports:
    shiny (>= 1.7.0),
    shinyAce (>= 0.4.0)
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
